  "title": "Warehouse Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Brief Summary</strong></p><p><ul><li>Basic <strong>up $2800</strong></li><li><strong>Allowance $200</strong></li><li>Day Shift allowance $12/day</li><li>Night shift allowance $24/day</li><li>Work 4 days rest 3 days<br />7am-7pm/7pm-7am <u><strong>(can choose morning/night shift)</strong></u></li><li>AWS + VB (Attractive Bonuses)</li><li>Working Location: East area</li><li>Well known Global MNC- Company Expanding</li></ul></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle all inquiries related to <strong>inbound, outbound</strong>, and <strong>return shipments</strong></p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth <strong>order fulfillment</strong></p></li><li><p>Create orders in <strong>SAP and WMS systems</strong></p></li><li><p>Manage <strong>documentation </strong>flow and record keeping</p></li><li><p>Track and consolidate requirements for daily consumables</p></li><li><p>Provide accurate and timely reports to relevant teams and warehouse in-charge</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Min “O” Level</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Minimum 1 year of relevant experiences</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience in SAP/WMS</p></li></ul><p><br />Interested Applicants, kindly send your updated CV to <a href=\"tel:+65 8500 3939\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em><strong>+65 8500 3939</strong></em></a> or click on <em><strong>“APPLY NOW”.</strong></em></p><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</em><br /></p><p><strong>---------</strong></p><p>EA Personnel Name: Chin Jia Hui, Janice<br />EA Personnel No: R22107485<br />EA License No: 15C7752</p>",
